---------- 8. PLL Usage Summary (begin) ----------

Instance Name                 : pll_inst1
Resource                      : PLL_0
Reference Clock Resource      : GPIOL_20
Reference Clock Frequency     : 25.0000 MHz
Reference Clock Period        : 40.0000 ns
Multiplier (M)                : 32
Pre-Divider (N)               : 1
VCO Frequency                 : 800.0000 MHz
Post-Divider (O)              : 4
PLL Frequency                 : 200.0000 MHz

Output Clock 0
Clock Pin Name                : pll_clk
Output Divider                : 4
Output Frequency              : 50.0000 MHz
Output Period                 : 20.000 ns

Frequency calculations:
	VCO = REFCLK * (M/N)
	    = 25.0000 MHz * (32/1)
	    = 800.0000 MHz
	PLL = VCO / O
	    = 800.0000 MHz / 4
	    = 200.0000 MHz

	CLKOUT0 = PLL / CLKOUT0_DIV
	        = 200.0000 MHz / 4
	        = 50.0000 MHz

SDC Constraints:
	create_clock -period 20.000 -name pll_clk [get_ports {pll_clk}]

